<h1>Noncense</h1>



<div id="description">
  <p>1987</p>

<p>“Knowledge of physical science will not console me for ignorance of morality in a time of affliction, but knowledge of morality will always console me for ignorance of physical science.”—Blaise&nbsp;Pascal</p>

